if the minefields have been cleared.

02:10:36.520 --> 02:10:37.820
Could the minefields
have been cleared?

02:10:37.820 --> 02:10:39.210
Well, you need to take Gallipoli.

02:10:39.210 --> 02:10:40.870
Could you have taken Gallipoli?

02:10:40.870 --> 02:10:44.410
Well, you could have done if
you of had more men, okay,

02:10:44.410 --> 02:10:47.450
and if you of had more
resources, better planning,

02:10:47.450 --> 02:10:49.130
more opportunity to do that.

02:10:49.130 --> 02:10:51.000
Because once those men
are punched through,

02:10:51.000 --> 02:10:52.320
