02:15:06.310 --> 02:15:09.690
Are there any specifically
aimed at Ryan?

02:15:09.690 --> 02:15:16.390
&gt;&gt; Ryan, it wasn't part of your
talk, but when we were in Belgium

02:15:16.390 --> 02:15:24.630
in the [Inaudible], one of the
