02:16:15.130 --> 02:16:17.430
Thank you for the question.

02:16:18.850 --> 02:16:23.250
One of the reasons that we see
the Germans being, in fact,

02:16:23.250 --> 02:16:28.550
very brutal towards the Belgians
is the von Schlieffen plan required

02:16:28.550 --> 02:16:32.880
them to move so quickly
through Belgium

02:16:32.880 --> 02:16:36.310
to their final objective,
which was Paris.

02:16:36.310 --> 02:16:38.980 position:56%
The Belgians put up a tough defense.

02:16:38.980 --> 02:16:41.420
I mentioned some of the forts that
they had and the money they had.

02:16:41.420 --> 02:16:44.190 position:56%
They could punch above their weight.

02:16:44.190 --> 02:16:49.880
They were very angry by being
delayed, and that they felt

02:16:49.880 --> 02:16:52.470
that the Belgians should
have just capitulated

02:16:52.470 --> 02:16:55.360
and allowed their troops
to go through.

02:16:55.360 --> 02:16:58.290
And so, this is one of the
reasons that they started

02:16:58.290 --> 02:17:01.420
to exact revenge upon the Belgians.

02:17:01.420 --> 02:17:05.920
And they were also looking back
to the Franco-Prussian War,

02:17:05.920 --> 02:17:11.580
in which the Belgians had irregular
troops, meaning no uniform,

02:17:11.580 --> 02:17:15.170
taking pot shots, sniper
shots at German troops.

02:17:15.170 --> 02:17:17.720
German troops before
the invasion were told,

02:17:17.720 --> 02:17:19.530
"The Belgians are probably
going to do this again,"

02:17:19.530 --> 02:17:21.940
which we understand they did not.

02:17:21.940 --> 02:17:23.880
But anytime they would
hear a rifle shot,

02:17:23.880 --> 02:17:26.540
they'd say, "Hey, Belgian sniper."

02:17:26.540 --> 02:17:30.290
They would round up communities
and have summary executions.

02:17:30.290 --> 02:17:33.700
So it was a mix of the
plan and then the mindset

02:17:33.700 --> 02:17:35.920
that the German troops
had before going in.

02:17:35.920 --> 02:17:38.920
I think that's the best way to
answer it, and it was very brutal,

02:17:38.920 --> 02:17:41.450
because war is a brutal thing.

02:17:41.450 --> 02:17:46.660
Also when they were starving from
the blockade, which I mentioned,

02:17:46.660 --> 02:17:49.090
that "We're not going to
get the Belgians food.

02:17:49.090 --> 02:17:51.890
It's going to come to Germany."

02:17:51.890 --> 02:17:53.190
