can't progress but it's more complex

02:18:22.510 --> 02:18:25.630
than that because as the Anzacs
came ashore, not only did they get

02:18:25.630 --> 02:18:27.980
up into that Pluggie
Plateau and face the ridge,

02:18:27.980 --> 02:18:30.340
